      takeaways: ["A customer platform coordinates governed facts; it should not become an unrestricted global data dump.", "Separate IAM, profile, consent, identity resolution, and analytical projections by ownership and purpose.", "Home-region writes, sanitized version events, deny-first privacy controls, and consumer receipts make distribution defensible."],
